{"tid":1556182,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"免費補通識（小組形式）","createTime":"2019-09-09T15:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T05:13:40.000Z","uid":153797,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fb668905fb6e43f1af6e73c87e518ec4b4ca81eb","tid":1556182,"uid":153797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:35:29.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我係一位通識導師，幾年前已經有係高登開POST同大家搞下通識，都試過開一D小組班以一人幾十蚊既價格上一堂通識（隨便起底）。但係呢幾個月，我一直出去撈發夢既同學仔，冷氣軍師下，以及企係中後，由於廢中心態，覺得自己一直都出唔到太多力。<br />\n<br />\n  所以，我想再次開番呢個通識班，免費幫發夢／有困難既同學仔，補習通識，幫你地順利去到應考DSE ，或者幫中五同學仔補底。呢幾年任教既學校都遍港九，主力教同學仔做操卷班同補底訓練，唔算成績標青，但都幫過唔少同學仔過關。<br />\n<br />\n  如果你真係有需要，就PM左我問左先，我地先再交換TG 。<br />\n  <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油！</span></span>"},{"pid":"d9d804f7d8e3e9ef0ba17cde48c37d83f84aa2c9","tid":1556182,"uid":218793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:37:15.000Z","msg":"連登冇pm 要直接留tg<br />\nBtw幫推"},{"pid":"e0ed0151ef4603d843eeba3dffec52dc07b1e97b","tid":1556182,"uid":153797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9d804f7d8e3e9ef0ba17cde48c37d83f84aa2c9","tid":1556182,"uid":218793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:37:15.000Z","msg":"連登冇pm 要直接留tg<br />\nBtw幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:40:14.000Z","msg":".....呀！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n我仲停留左係高登年代....<br />\n<br />\nTG：kitkit1989"},{"pid":"e0191668d4cc12a0194aceab9c7d5a7ee945d8f0","tid":1556182,"uid":153797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"b7733e9cb16dc809fbea812fcd49a07af291ff32","tid":1556182,"uid":135060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:44:34.000Z","msg":"石sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac742462141f8